### Test Review System API Endpoints

### 1. Test: Create Review with Offer
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/review/add-review
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "offerId": 1,
  "ratingValue": 5,
  "reviewComment": "Amazing experience!",
  "reviewedUserId": null
}

### 2. Test: Create Direct User-to-User Review
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/review/add-review
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "offerId": null,
  "ratingValue": 4,
  "reviewComment": "Great person to work with!",
  "reviewedUserId": "{{user2Id}}"
}

### 3. Test: Get Reviews by User ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/review/get-user-reviews?userId={{userId}}&pageNumber=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Test: Get Reviews by Offer ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/review/get-offer-reviews?offerId=1&pageNumber=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Test: Get Reviews Between Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/review/get-reviews-between-users?user1Id={{user1Id}}&user2Id={{user2Id}}&pageNumber=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Test: Get All Reviews (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/review/get-all-reviews-admin?pageNumber=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Variables for testing:
# @baseUrl = https://localhost:7001
# @token = your_jwt_token_here
# @adminToken = your_admin_jwt_token_here
# @userId = user_guid_here
# @user1Id = user1_guid_here
# @user2Id = user2_guid_here 